<section data-scrollax-parent="true">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
            <div class="section-subtitle">Discover &amp; Connect </div>
            <span class="section-separator"></span>
            <p>It's simple. You do the search, we do the hard work! You type in the city, we bring you the most suitable places.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-wrap fl-wrap">
            <ul class="no-list-style">
                <li>
                    <div class="process-item">
                        <span class="process-count">01 </span>
                        <div class="time-line-icon"><i class="fal fa-map-marker-alt"></i></div>
                        <h4> Browse through the latest and greatest of our ever-expanding catalogue of places!</h4>
                        <p>Do you want to search by city? We' ve got you covered! Do you want to search by name? We' ve got you covered! Do you want to search by price? Guess what... </p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="pr-dec"></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="process-item">
                        <span class="process-count">02</span>
                        <div class="time-line-icon"><i class="fal fa-mail-bulk"></i></div>
                        <h4> Contact a Few Owners</h4>
                        <p>Have questions about your booking? Want to know more information about a place? Get in touch with the owner directly through our platform and ask them!</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="pr-dec"></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="process-item">
                        <span class="process-count">03</span>
                        <div class="time-line-icon"><i class="fal fa-layer-plus"></i></div>
                        <h4> Make a Listing</h4>
                        <p>Are you a home owner and looking to rent your place? Well, look no more. Add your place to our ever-growing catalogue of available places and we will make sure that everyone sees it.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="process-end"><i class="fal fa-check"></i></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!--section end-->
